epic crushing groove devestation ... ! ! ! by the time that you get too the 2nd track on 'the red sea'it is too late.. you are quickly subjected to unmercyful desolet fury ... i can not express enough , the hoplessness , and desperic rage that this song displays ! ! ! the vocals are so incredible it sends me into a barbaric slam groove frenzy every time i hear it..this song has the most pummeling crushing spiteful slamming hatered filled breakdowns of any band in the scene..long live sludge cruch slam groove hatered.. ! ! ! i rate this album 100 stars ! ! ! !